Pre requirements:

1. Install MySQL server
2. Configure the connection in server.js 
    host: 'yourhost',
    user: 'yourusername',
    password: 'yourpassword',
3. Run the notes_db_script.sql script in server/ folder
4. npm i on server and clients folder
5. Start the server and client


Note:
Attempted to install Draftjs word count plugin but it was causing some error, hence I removed it
https://www.npmjs.com/package/@draft-js-plugins/counter